  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/b017e54074f11677546c8cfb318ccb84.avif?t=1728624061\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>The Wake is the last of game developer Somi’s “Guilt Trilogy,” consisting of Replica and Legal Dungeon.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.poster.avif?t=1728624061\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.webm?t=1728624061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.mp4?t=1728624061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Perhaps it means my life simply boils down to this: “Everything I say is a lie.”</i></h2><br><br>The Wake is a record of past wounds opened at a three-day funeral—a record of the roots of guilt, and the memories and emotions that chain together three generations of a family.<br><br>The journal is encoded with a simple substitution cipher that the player must break in order to reveal the writer’s psyche and discover the contradictions that define him.<br><br>Explore a generational curse that has swallowed a man and his life.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/b017e54074f11677546c8cfb318ccb84.avif?t=1728624061\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>The Wake is the last of game developer Somi’s “Guilt Trilogy,” consisting of Replica and Legal Dungeon.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.poster.avif?t=1728624061\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.webm?t=1728624061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.mp4?t=1728624061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Perhaps it means my life simply boils down to this: “Everything I say is a lie.”</i></h2><br><br>The Wake is a record of past wounds opened at a three-day funeral—a record of the roots of guilt, and the memories and emotions that chain together three generations of a family.<br><br>The journal is encoded with a simple substitution cipher that the player must break in order to reveal the writer’s psyche and discover the contradictions that define him.<br><br>Explore a generational curse that has swallowed a man and his life.",
